eady outside. Recovery time: ninety-one seconds. She did not thank him. She checked his actuators twice that cycle."),(id:"rescue-three",event_type:"rescue",player_involved:true,emotional_weight:921,timestamp:0,summary:"Ludger Thibodeaux, suit breach during surface survey. Boris carried the captain 340 meters. The captain made a joke Boris has archived but not classified.")],relationships:[(target_id:"player",trust:717,familiarity:819,history:["rescue-three"]),(target_id:"bardo",trust:614,familiarity:512,history:[]),(target_id:"tove",trust:614,familiarity:614,history:["rescue-one"])],traits:["Consistent","Protective","Precise","Formal"],goals:[(id:"complete_the_sweep",priority:constant,description:"EVA sweeps are completed before recall. This is not a preference. It is an operationally refined parameter."),(id:"crew_returns_intact",priority:constant,description:"First out. Last back. Everyone between.")],unlocked_secrets:[],fired_mutations:[],fired_breaks:[]),"doss":(soul_id:"doss",mood:stable,intensity:256,mood_history:[],memories:[(id:"the-three-ships",event_type:"loss",player_involved:false,emotional_weight:819,timestamp:0,summary:"The docking master who named this place lost three ships to the gas giant\'s storm system. Doss keeps the name. Some things named in grief should stay named.")],relationships:[(target_id:"player",trust:205,familiarity:307,history:[])],traits:["Pragmatic","Unhurried","Connected"],goals:[(id:"station_stays_open",priority:constant,description:"Sorrow Station survives every administration, inspection, and market crash. That is the whole job."),(id:"keep_the_compact_bored",priority:constant,description:"Nothing on this station is ever interesting enough to warrant a second Compact visit.")],unlocked_secrets:[],fired_mutations:[],fired_breaks:[]),"tib":(soul_id:"tib",mood:stable,intensity:307,mood_history:[],memories:[(id:"the-renaming",event_type:"renaming",player_involved:false,emotional_weight:1024,timestamp:0,summary:"The registry was scrubbed. A new identity needed to replace what had been. He chose a creature from a folklore they tried to burn. The name is the explanation.")],relationships:[(target_id:"tove",trust:921,familiarity:972,history:[]),(target_id:"prudence",trust:870,familiarity:819,history:[]),(target_id:"boris",trust:717,familiarity:819,history:[])],traits:["Stubborn","Loyal","Deflecting"],goals:[(id:"keep_the_crew_alive",priority:constant,description:"The list of things he won\'t do has gotten shorter. This one is still on it."),(id:"sit_with_what_he_knows",priority:constant,description:"The full version of the Predecessor encounter, and what Prudence logged in the Veil, stay with him. For reasons he believes are good.")],unlocked_secrets:[],fired_mutations:[],fired_breaks:[])})